Paris Hilton.

61
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:47,860
That's a low blow.

62
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:49,420
But not the worst.

63
00:02:49,420 --> 00:02:51,280
Who else is criticizing Trump,

64
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,849
