65
00:02:53,849 --> 00:02:57,610
Why it's my favorite state-run media, Global
Times!

66
00:02:57,610 --> 00:03:00,409
Yes, Chinese media is calling Donald Trump,

67
00:03:00,409 --> 00:03:05,069
