US election politics.

81
00:03:36,769 --> 00:03:39,290
Likewise, for Chinese media,

82
00:03:39,290 --> 00:03:43,230
Trump is the perfect way to attack the evil
American boogeyman:

83
00:03:43,230 --> 00:03:44,129
democracy.

84
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:48,019
For years, the Communist Party has taken the
line that

85
00:03:48,019 --> 00:03:51,400
Chinese people simply aren't ready for democracy.

86
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:54,989
Which is why they should be under an authoritarian
rule instead.

87
00:03:54,989 --> 00:03:58,849
And now, the Communist Party is using Trump
to make their point.

88
00:03:58,849 --> 00:04:01,340
They highlight fistfights at Trump rallies
as proof

89
00:04:01,340 --> 00:04:05,959
